    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-weight:900;font-size:clamp(19px,2.8vw,27px);letter-spacing:-.03em;color:var(--text);line-height:1.1;margin-bottom:10px;">
      Common Questions About Shopify Automation in 2026
    </h2>
    <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-3);max-width:640px;margin-bottom:0;">
      Answers to the most common questions Shopify merchants have about automation, tracking, and free tool replacements in 2026.
    </p>
    <div class="gp-faq-grid">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-q">How do I fix Shopify Meta ROAS dropping in 2026?</div>
        <div class="faq-a">Three changes converged in Q1 2026 to break Meta tracking: iOS 26's Link Tracking Protection, Shopify's January 13 pixel default switching to Optimized mode, and Meta's algorithm shift. Fix: switch App Pixel to Always On in Settings → Customer Events, set Meta data sharing to Maximum, and implement server-side CAPI via Make.com. <strong>Most stores recover 20–40% of missing conversions within 7–14 days.</strong> The full guide is <a href="https://stackarchitect.xyz/blog/shopify-meta-roas-dropped-2026-fix">free here</a>.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-q">What replaces Shopify Stocky after it shuts down August 31 2026?</div>
        <div class="faq-a"><strong>Stocky Swap</strong> is a free Make.com webhook that automatically logs every Shopify order to a Google Sheet you own — no vendor lock-in, no monthly fees. Deploys in 4 minutes on any Shopify plan. Shopify Stocky was removed from the App Store February 2, 2026. Any inventory data not exported before August 31 will be permanently deleted. The <a href="https://stackarchitect.xyz/blog/the-ultimate-guide-to-shopify-inventory-management">Ultimate Inventory Guide</a> covers the complete free system including stock alerts, supplier tracking, and velocity analysis.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-q">What is the best free Klaviyo alternative for Shopify in 2026?</div>
        <div class="faq-a"><strong>Systeme.io provides 2,000 contacts and unlimited email sends permanently at $0/month</strong> — including sales funnels, CRM, and affiliate management. For stores over 2,000 contacts, <a href={aff.getresponse} rel="noopener sponsored">GetResponse</a> starts at $19/month vs Klaviyo's $100/month at 5,000 contacts, with equivalent abandoned cart, welcome, and post-purchase flows.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-q">How does TikTok Events API work with Shopify?</div>
        <div class="faq-a">TikTok's Events API sends purchase events server-to-server via Make.com, bypassing iOS restrictions. <strong>The critical detail: TikTok's purchase event is called CompletePayment — not "Purchase".</strong> Using the wrong name sends events to the wrong category in Events Manager. You cannot change pixel mode after creation, so verify before starting. EMQ scores of 6–8 are achievable.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-q">Is Make.com actually free for Shopify automation?</div>
        <div class="faq-a">Yes. Make.com's free plan gives 1,000 operations per month — 10× more than Zapier's 100 free tasks — including webhook triggers and HTTP modules. <strong>One Shopify Order Payment webhook can simultaneously branch to Meta CAPI, Google Enhanced Conversions, TikTok Events API, Google Sheets inventory, and P&amp;L.</strong> Most stores under 250 orders/month run the complete stack free indefinitely.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-q">Can Tidio replace Gorgias for Shopify customer support?</div>
        <div class="faq-a">Yes. <a href={aff.tidio} rel="noopener sponsored">Tidio's</a> Lyro AI resolves approximately 70% of inbound Shopify support queries automatically — order status, shipping, product FAQs — without human intervention. <a href={aff.gorgias} rel="noopener sponsored">Gorgias</a> costs £60–£300/month. Tidio's permanently functional free tier covers 50 Lyro AI conversations/month. Setup takes 30 minutes.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-q">What are Shopify Agentic Storefronts?</div>
        <div class="faq-a">Shopify Agentic Storefronts enable your products to be purchased directly inside ChatGPT, Google AI Mode, and Microsoft Copilot without the customer leaving those AI interfaces. <strong>Currently US-only and in early access.</strong> Preparation steps — Knowledge Base App, product data optimisation, FAQ schema — apply to all stores immediately and improve AI search discoverability regardless of eligibility.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-q">How do I track Shopify profit and loss for free?</div>
        <div class="faq-a">A Make.com webhook auto-populates revenue, COGS, Shopify transaction fees, and net profit into a Google Sheet for every order within 60 seconds of purchase. <strong>Every P&amp;L app charges $25–$299/month.</strong> If CAPI Shield or Stocky Swap is already deployed, this adds a single branch to your existing scenario — setup takes under 3 minutes.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-q">How do I fix iOS conversion tracking on Shopify in 2026?</div>
        <div class="faq-a">iOS updates since 2021 have cumulatively broken 30–60% of browser-based conversion tracking. The fix is server-side tracking via Conversions API — purchase events sent server-to-server bypass iOS restrictions entirely. <strong>Switch your Shopify App Pixel to Always On mode (5 minutes), then implement CAPI Shield for full server-side coverage (2–3 hours).</strong> The full diagnosis guide covers each iOS change specifically: <a href="https://stackarchitect.xyz/blog/how-to-fix-shopify-conversion-tracking-after-ios-updates">How to Fix Shopify Conversion Tracking After iOS Updates</a>.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-q">Which Shopify apps are a waste of money in 2026?</div>
        <div class="faq-a">The most commonly overpaid-for apps: <strong>Elevar ($199/mo) and Triple Whale ($129–$299/mo)</strong> for server-side tracking — replaced free by CAPI Shield. <strong>Zapier ($49/mo)</strong> for automation — replaced free by Make.com with 10× more operations. <strong>Klaviyo ($150–$400/mo)</strong> for email under 2,000 contacts — replaced free by Systeme.io. <strong>BeProfit and TrueProfit ($19–$299/mo)</strong> for P&amp;L — replaced free by P&amp;L Auto. Full breakdown: <a href="https://stackarchitect.xyz/blog/shopify-apps-that-are-a-waste-of-money">Shopify Apps That Are a Waste of Money</a>.</div>
      </div>
